      "full_name": "Joint Stock Company “Research Institute of Communication and Control Systems”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "JSC “Research Institute of Communication and Control Systems” (JSC NIISSU) is a Russian military industry company and part of the JSC Sozvezdie Concern, and is therefore ultimately part of the State Corporation Rostec. JSC NIISSU is involved in the development of military equipment, as it develops and supplies complexes and elements of digital ground-level communication systems and of automated control systems to the military of the Russian Federation. JSC NIISSU is therefore supporting materially Russia’s military and industrial complex and the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}